The Map With No Name:

This is the first map I made for CS:Source, way back when.  It wasn't intended to be serious, I just wanted to fiddle around with the new Hammer.  Somehow, it ended up becoming a server favorite anyway.  Apparently, what it lacks in flash it makes up for in gameplay.  I'm not looking for scores or critique here--I make *actual* maps nowadays--I just wanted to share.  Besides, it seems the majority of players prefer "lesser" maps like this one... :(

I wish I could say for sure how many spawns there are, but I don't know...I'd guess 32.
